turns.ai_line: Good morning, doctor. I dey feel serious pain for my belle after I chop some leftover rice yesterday. I just dey vomit and the running stomach no let me rest. This kind wahala never happen before o.
"Abeg doctor, wetin you think say dey cause this kind wahala? I just dey pray say make e no be say I chop spoil food. I no fit bear this kind pain again o."

Doctor, I dey suspect say na the leftover rice wey I chop na im cause this problem. I remember say I no warm am well before I chop. E go better make you check me well make we know whether na food poisoning. I no fit stand this pain o.
